1940;;Pack Up Your Troubles;;British;;Oswald Mitchell;;Reginald Purdell, Wylie Watson;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pack_Up_Your_Troubles_(1940_film);;Garage owner Tommy (Reginald Purdell) and ventriloquist friend Eric (Wylie Watson) join the army and travel to France, where they are captured by the Nazis. However, Eric's voice-throwing skills come in handy in engineering their escape and in obtaining top secret information.